# Accessibility

- Semantic HTML first; interactive elements must be keyboard accessible
- Every form control needs an accessible name
- Manage focus in dialogs/overlays; announce dynamic changes when needed
- No clickable non-semantic elements without full a11y contract

Call MCP `get_standards_section` with `accessibility` before shipping UI changes.
